{"tid":142332,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"伯伯警署前過路遭巴士撞頭命危 司機涉不顧而去","createTime":"2017-03-03T16:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-03T16:32:43.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8f42c3a7584cc3dc61553e99582270ee7d1225b3","tid":142332,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:03:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: violet;\"><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong>伯伯警署前過路遭巴士撞頭命危 司機涉不顧而去<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170303/56381508\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170303%2F56381508&d=I5RPnmyQkmy%2BYB%2FsDyc%2BvzOU%2Fspzl0GStOx2So8CiJ8%3D&h=1f93c624\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.apple.nextmedia.com%2Frealtime%2Fbreaking%2F20170303%2F56381508&h=49bfd49c\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.apple.nextmedia.com/realtime/breaking/20170303/56381508</a></strong></div></span><br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴發生一宗不顧而去的車禍。傍晚6時許，一名76歲姓郭伯伯沿彌敦道行走，至近尖沙嘴警署對開橫過馬路時，遭一輛往旺角方向的巴士車尾撞中受傷，但司機在傷者倒地後未有停車，繼續開車駛離現場，有途人見狀報警。救護車接報到場，接載陷入昏迷的傷者至伊利沙伯醫院治理，警方正翻查附近天眼，追查涉事巴士下落。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170303/large/1488540939_578f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170303%2Flarge%2F1488540939_578f.jpg&h=73dd2e82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n警方事後封鎖部分路段調查，地上遺下一灘血迹。(司徒韋桐攝)"},{"pid":"6943f82f3e9fe7bdd367164eaf1024ef3db98a35","tid":142332,"uid":33907,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:07:36.000Z","msg":"？？車尾 巴士倒後行？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f2117e4acb0c2bb26e026bde61fe3f950a5c8ed","tid":142332,"uid":20058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-03T16:08:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>？？車尾 巴士倒後行？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n轉彎掛<img